price: (Yaa Muhammad!) Ati Mu’uminoota ta’uu dhabuu isaaniitiif [gaddaan] lubbuu kee baasuun siif sodaatama.
arabic: لَعَلَّكَ بَٰخِعٞ نَّفۡسَكَ أَلَّا يَكُونُواْ مُؤۡمِنِينَ

version.title: Oromo translation
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Oromo by Ghaly Ababour Abaghuna, printed in 2009.

meta.transliteration: laʿallaka bākhiʿun nafsaka allā yakūnū mu'minīna
